==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: citizens band
<hw>citizens' band</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>that portion of the radio
frequency spectrum allocated by the FCC for the use of individual
citizens for short-distance personal or business use, from either fixed
or mobile stations. Abbreviated <abbr>CB</abbr>. Called also
<altname>Citizens Radio Service</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Citizenship</ent>⟦br⟧
